-- Akbank Appoints Binbasgil as Acting CEO, Replacing Akkurt
-- B y   E r c a n   E r s o y
-- 2012-01-05T16:01:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-05/akbank-appoints-binbasgil-as-acting-ceo-replacing-akkurt.html
Akbank TAS (AKBNK) , the Turkish bank part-
owned by  Citigroup Inc. (C) , said it appointed Sabri Hakan Binbasgil
as acting chief executive officer, replacing Ziya Akkurt.  Binbasgil was previously deputy CEO, Akbank said in a 
filing with the Istanbul Stock Exchange today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ercan Ersoy in Istanbul at 
 eersoy@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
